375
00:32:26,840 --> 00:32:27,880
Mau quay lại đây!

376
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:28,840
Phượng Ẩn!

377
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:57,440
Nếu cô vẫn kính trọng Lan Phong,

378
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:02,840
